e in the line-of-sight direction.\nThe cancellation process repeats again and again. Eventually the fan-spine dome\nis destroyed and a new connectivity is formed. We suggest that magnetic\nreconnection between the EFR and the magnetic fields of the fan-spine dome in\nthe process is responsible for the destruction of the dome.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2015 02:39:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 May 2015 09:35:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-11"}
